author: Graeme Campbell
title: NikeLab x UNDERCOVER GYAKUSOU’s Spring ’17 Collection Is Crammed With Innovation
text:
Visit the original post to see all 13 images from this gallery. 
Brand: NikeLab x UNDERCOVER GYAKUSOU.
Season: Spring 2017.
Key Pieces: The sash-design technical windbreaker packs some heavy roadman vibes, while those “Oreo” LunarEpic Low Flyknit 2s look way too tasty to be wasted on the running track.
Editor’s Notes: Jun Takahashi’s long-term NikeLab partnership rolls into 2017 with a performance range that combines asymmetrical aesthetics with Nike’s latest running innovations — including Nike Dri-FIT and Nike AeroReact. If this doesn’t get you up off the couch and back out running in time for summer then nothing will.
FIND OUT MORE Staying with The Swoosh, NikeLab x Riccardo Tisci are working on a special Air Max ’97 Mid .
